        "text": "## Ni²⁺ Binding: Ammonia vs. Ethylenediamine\n\nHere is a direct comparison of the first stepwise stability constant (log K₁) for Ni²⁺ with each ligand at 25 °C, from NIST SRD-46:\n\n| Ligand | Reaction | log K₁ | T (°C) | I (M) |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Ammonia (NH₃) | Ni²⁺ + NH₃ ⇌ [Ni(NH₃)]²⁺ | **2.72** | 25 | 0 |\n| Ethylenediamine (en) | Ni²⁺ + en ⇌ [Ni(en)]²⁺ | **7.32** | 25 | 0 |",
